# A [[piston engine]] driven by steam (as contrasted, for example, with a [[steam turbine]]).
# Any [[heat engine]] that uses steam as its primary working fluid to do [[mechanical]] [[work]].
# {{lb|en|British}} A [[steam locomotive]].

